Package com.orchestranetworks.addon.dataexchange

Classes and interfaces to call Data Exchange import, export and transfer data.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
DataExchangeExport This interface defines a Data Exchange Export action with given specifications.
DataExchangeImport This interface defines a Data Exchange Import action with given specifications.
DataExchangeTransferData This interface defines a Data Exchange 'Transfer data' execution with given specifications.
 

Class Summary
DataExchangeDataAccessSpec A representation of a Data Exchange data access specification.
DataExchangeExportDataAccessSpec A representation of a data access specification for the Data Exchange Export service.
DataExchangeExportResult This class defines Data Exchange Export service's export result.
DataExchangeExportSpec This class stores specifications for export services and includes the export type, target application logical name and target application version.
DataExchangeExportType This class defines all Data Exchange export types.
DataExchangeFactory This singleton initializes Data Exchange executions including Export, Import and Transferring data.
DataExchangeImportMode This class defines all import modes of Data Exchange Import services.
DataExchangeImportResult This class defines a Data Exchange Import service import result.
DataExchangeImportSpec This class stores specifications for import services including import type and import mode.
DataExchangeImportType This class defines all import types used for Data Exchange Import services.
DataExchangeSpec A representation of a Data Exchange specification which stores a Data Exchange data access specification (DataExchangeDataAccessSpec) and a list of table paths.
DataExchangeTransferOption This class defines all options that are used for the transfer data service.
DataExchangeTransferSpec This class stores specifications for transferring data execution.
DataExchangeTransferType This class defines all transfer types that are used for the Transfer data service.
DataResult This class stores data results and includes the number of created, deleted, updated or invalid records.
 

Exception Summary
DataExchangeException This class defines a DataExchange add-on exception.
 

Package com.orchestranetworks.addon.dataexchange Description

Classes and interfaces to call Data Exchange import, export and transfer data.
